NBA ALL-STAR WEEKEND
February 16, 2007
Adam Morrison
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT







 Q.  Can you talk about your first All-Star experience? 
 ADAM MORRISON:  It's been good so far.  I'm having fun and it's cool being in Vegas. 

 Q.  What about being here as part of the Agassi Prep? 
 ADAM MORRISON:  It's cool.  It's cool opening up a new gym for kids. 
 So it's fun to get in here and show the kids that we work hard. 

 Q.  What's the best part so far about your rookie season with the Bobcats? 
 ADAM MORRISON:  Just going through the NBA season, experiencing everything firsthand is really cool. 



END_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT